---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="For Fundraising — CloakShare" description="Track which investors actually read your pitch deck. Slide-by-slide analytics, dynamic watermarks, email gating, and link expiry. Free tier available." canonical="/for/fundraising">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-mono text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Use Case</p>
      <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-4xl text-foreground mb-4">For Fundraising</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary font-sans text-lg mb-16 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Track which investors actually read your deck — not just who clicked the link.
        Slide-by-slide analytics, real-time notifications, and dynamic watermarks let you
        follow up at the right time with the right investors.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Slide-by-slide analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            See exactly which slides each investor spent time on. Know if they lingered on
            the financials or skipped straight to the team page. Page-level dwell time, not
            just open/close.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7.864 4.243A7.5 7.5 0 0119.5 10.5c0 2.92-.556 5.709-1.568 8.268M5.742 6.364A7.465 7.465 0 004.5 10.5a48.667 48.667 0 00-1.418 8.773 .75.75 0 00.665.836c3.976.478 8.03.478 12.006 0a.75.75 0 00.665-.836A48.78 48.78 0 0015 10.5a7.465 7.465 0 00-1.242-4.136m-9.016.496A7.466 7.466 0 0112 3c2.157 0 4.126.911 5.508 2.372" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Dynamic watermarks</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Every page watermarked with the investor's email and timestamp. If your deck
            leaks during due diligence, trace it to the source. Canvas-rendered,
            non-removable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Email gating + link expiry</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Require investors to verify their email before viewing. Set links to expire
            after the round closes. Revoke access to any link instantly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Real-time notifications</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Get webhook notifications the moment an investor opens your deck. Know when to
            follow up — while they're still thinking about it, not two days later.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 bg-surface border border-accent/30 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-accent mb-4">Built for your fundraise</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">No per-seat pricing — share with 50 investors without paying per viewer</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">No visit limits — DocSend caps you at 100 views then forces an upgrade</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">Video support — send a Loom-style product demo alongside your deck</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">Self-host option for stealth-mode startups who need full data control</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">Free tier includes 50 links and 500 views — enough for an angel round</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="https://app.cloakshare.dev/register" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-accent text-background font-mono font-semibold text-sm rounded-md hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors">
          Share your first deck free
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-tertiary font-sans mt-3">Free tier: 50 links, 500 views per month</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
